cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.SY

The paper deals with measuring the delay in video transmission, which involves aspects of multimedia (cs.MM), networked systems (cs.NI), computer vision (cs.CV), information theory (cs.IT), and control systems (cs.SY). However, since the focus is on measuring delay in video communication, we believe that cs.MM and cs.NI are the most likely categories, followed by cs.CV, cs.IT, and cs.SY.
